solution:
解 (1)

$$
\begin{gathered}
L=-m c^{2} \sqrt{1-\frac{1}{c^{2}}\left(\dot{r}^{2}+r^{2} \dot{\varphi}^{2}\right)}+\frac{G M m}{r} \\
\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{r}}=\frac{m \dot{r}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}, \quad \frac{\partial L}{\partial r}=\frac{m r \dot{\varphi}^{2}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}-\frac{G M m}{r^{2}} \\
\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{\varphi}}=\frac{m r^{2} \dot{\varphi}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}, \quad \frac{\partial L}{\partial \varphi}=0
\end{gathered}
$$

其中 $v^{2}=\dot{r}^{2}+r^{2} \dot{\varphi}^{2}$ ，

\begin{gather*}
\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{~d} t}\left(\frac{m \dot{r}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}\right)-\left(\frac{m r \dot{\varphi}^{2}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}-\frac{G M m}{r^{2}}\right)=0  \tag{1}\\
\frac{m r^{2} \dot{\varphi}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}=J(\text { 常量 }) \tag{2}
\end{gather*}

将式（2）代入式（1），得

\begin{equation*}
\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{~d} t}\left(\frac{J \dot{r}}{r^{2} \dot{\varphi}}\right)-\frac{J \dot{\varphi}}{r}+\frac{G M m}{r^{2}}=0 \tag{3}
\end{equation*}

令 $u=\frac{1}{r}, r=\frac{1}{u}, \dot{r}=-\frac{1}{u^{2}} \dot{u}, \frac{\dot{r}}{r^{2}}=-\dot{u}$,

$$
\frac{\mathrm{d}^2 u}{\mathrm{~d} \varphi^2}=\frac{\mathrm{d} u}{\mathrm{~d} \varphi} \dot{\varphi}
$$

式（3）可化成

\begin{equation*}
\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} u}{\mathrm{~d} \varphi^{2}}+u=\frac{G M m}{J \dot{\varphi}} u^{2} \tag{4}
\end{equation*}

因为 $\frac{\partial L}{\partial t}=0$,

$$
\begin{gathered}
\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{r}} \dot{r}+\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{\varphi}} \dot{\varphi}-L=E(\text { 常量 }) \\
\frac{m \dot{r}^{2}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}-\frac{m r^{2} \dot{\varphi}^{2}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}+m c^{2} \sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}-\frac{G M m}{r}=E
\end{gathered}
$$

可得

\begin{align*}
& \frac{m c^{2}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}-\frac{G M m}{r}=E \\
& \frac{m c^{2}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}=E+G M m u \tag{5}
\end{align*}

由式（2），

\begin{equation*}
\dot{\varphi}=\frac{J}{m} \sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}} u^{2} \tag{6}
\end{equation*}

用式（5）、（6），式（4）可改写为

\begin{equation*}
\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} u}{\mathrm{~d} \varphi^{2}}+\left[1-\left(\frac{G M m}{J c}\right)^{2}\right] u=\frac{G M m E}{J^{2} c^{2}} \tag{7}
\end{equation*}

令

$$
u^{\prime}=u-\frac{\frac{G M m E}{J^{2} c^{2}}}{1-\left(\frac{G M m}{J c}\right)^{2}}=u-\frac{G M m E}{(J c)^{2}-(G M m)^{2}}
$$

式（7）化成

$$
\begin{gathered}
\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} u^{\prime}}{\mathrm{d} \varphi^{2}}+\left[1-\left(\frac{G M m}{J c}\right)^{2}\right] u^{\prime}=0 \\
u^{\prime}=A \cos \left[\alpha\left(\varphi-\varphi_{0}\right)\right]
\end{gathered}
$$

其中

$$
\alpha=\left[1-\left(\frac{G M m}{J c}\right)^{2}\right]^{\frac{1}{2}}
$$

$A 、 \varphi_{0}$ 为常量.

$$
u=\frac{G M m E}{(J c)^{2}-(G M m)^{2}}+A \cos \left[\alpha\left(\varphi-\varphi_{0}\right)\right]
$$

$$
\frac{1}{r}=\frac{1}{r_{0}}+A \cos \left[\alpha\left(\varphi-\varphi_{0}\right)\right]
$$

其中

$$
\begin{gathered}
r_{0}=\frac{(J c)^{2}-(G M m)^{2}}{G M m E} \\
\frac{1}{r}=\frac{1}{r_{0}}\left\{1+\varepsilon \cos \left[\alpha\left(\varphi-\varphi_{0}\right)\right]\right\}
\end{gathered}
$$

其中 $\varepsilon=A r_{0}$ 。

