其动量变化为

\[
\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d} t}\left(\frac{m \mathbf{v}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}\right)=\mathbf{F}
\]

考虑到受力情况和初始条件，运动轨迹在 \( xy \) 平面上，分量方程为

\[
\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d} t}\left(\frac{m \dot{x}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}\right)=0, \quad \frac{\mathrm{~d}}{\mathrm{~d} t}\left(\frac{m \dot{y}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}\right)=F
\]

当 \( t=0 \) 时, \(\dot{x}=v_{0}\), \(\dot{y}=0\)。积分上述两式得

\[
\begin{gathered}
\frac{m \dot{x}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}=\frac{m v_{0}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v_{0}^{2}}{c^{2}}}}, \quad \frac{m \dot{y}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}=F t \\
\frac{\dot{x}^{2}+\dot{y}^{2}}{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}=\frac{v_{0}^{2}}{1-\frac{v_{0}^{2}}{c^{2}}}+\left(\frac{F t}{m}\right)^{2}
\end{gathered}
\]

因为 \(\dot{x}^{2}+\dot{y}^{2}=v^{2}\), 上式可改写为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& v^{2}=\left[\frac{v_{0}^{2}}{1-\frac{v_{0}^{2}}{c^{2}}}+\left(\frac{F t}{m}\right)^{2}\right]\left(1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}\right) \\
& v^{2}=\frac{k}{1+\frac{k}{c^{2}}}
\end{aligned}
\]

其中

\[
k=\frac{v_{0}^{2}}{1-\frac{v_{0}^{2}}{c^{2}}}+\left(\frac{F t}{m}\right)^{2}
\]

则

\[
1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}=\frac{c^{2}}{c^{2}+k}
\]

由此

\[
\begin{aligned}
\dot{x} &= \frac{v_{0}}{\sqrt{1-\left(\frac{v_{0}}{c}\right)^{2}}} \sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}=\frac{v_{0}}{\sqrt{1-\left(\frac{v_{0}}{c}\right)^{2}}} \sqrt{\frac{c^{2}}{c^{2}+k}} \\
\dot{y} &= \frac{F t}{m} \sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}=\frac{F t}{m} \sqrt{\frac{c^{2}}{c^{2}+k}}
\end{aligned}
\]

